Wendy Blacklock https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wendy_Blacklock 0 Wendy Blacklock AM (born 1932, Sydney, Australia) is a retired Australia-based theatre and radio actress and producer and television actress best known for her long-running role of comedy character dizzy Edith "Mummy" MacDonald in the 1970s television soap opera Number 96 ;
